The paper focuses on computer vision techniques for autonomous vehicles, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses machine learning methods (cs.LG) and end-to-end learning (cs.AI), as well as natural language processing for scene understanding (cs.CL). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely for this paper.
